DAY
1
(-/L/D)
Pick up at airport (or hotel), Transfer to Sa Pa, Visit Cat Cat Village, Shopping at night market Sapa, ON Sapa
DAY
2
(B/L/D)
Breakfast, Visit Fansipan (include Muong Hoa Train, Buffet Fansipan, Cable Car ticket), Visit Moana Cafe (not include cafe fee)
Optional Funicular Train Fansipan: $7 USD/pax up, $5 USD/pax down. (Ideal for elderly guests who wish to skip the 600-step climb to the peak).
Dinner (Salmon hotpot + redwine), ON Sapa
DAY
3
(B/L/D)
Breakfast, Back to Hanoi, Photo stop at Vietnam-China Border Gate, Tran Quoc Pagoda, Mega Grand World Ha Noi, Dinner, Ha Long night market, ON Halong Bay
DAY
4
(B/L)
A boat trip through Ha Long Bay, visiting Thien Cung Cave, Dinh Huong Islet, and Cock Fighting Islet, Lunch, Back to Ha Noi, Hanoi Old Quarter, Sword Lake Hanoi, Shopping, End of tour
